OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1779185247
OL,3,CWild beavers found following 'illegal
OL,4,Cand unauthorised releases'
OL,6,FA nature recovery programme has found
OL,7,Fwild beavers on the River Lowther in
OL,8,FEden for the first time in centuries.
OL,10,FCumbria Connect says the animals are
OL,11,F"believed to originate from illegal
OL,12,Fand unauthorised releases".
OL,14,FMartin Varley, programme manager for
OL,15,FCumbria Connect, told ITV Border:
OL,16,F"There's nowhere else these beavers
OL,17,Fcan come from, we can't magic them out
OL,18,Fof thin air.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1779185247
OL,3,CWild beavers found following 'illegal
OL,4,Cand unauthorised releases'
OL,6,F"The only way they could have got here
OL,7,Fis if someone has brought them in
OL,8,Fillegally."
OL,10,FThe discovery comes after signs of
OL,11,Fbeaver activity had been spotted
OL,12,Foutside of the Lowther Enclosure
OL,13,Fduring 2025.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1779185247
OL,3,CWild beavers found following 'illegal
OL,4,Cand unauthorised releases'
OL,6,FMr Varley said: "We hear a lot of
OL,7,Fstories, people tell us what they've
OL,8,Fseen, they're out walking their dog,
OL,9,Fso we've heard anecdotal stories and
OL,10,Fseen people's pictures of signs of
OL,11,Fbeavers on the river, which makes us
OL,12,Fthink there's probably at least one
OL,13,Ffamily in the catchment."
OL,15,FThe beavers are a protected species,
OL,16,Fwhich makes it an offence to capture,
OL,17,Fkill or disturb the animals or their
OL,18,Fresting places.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1779185247
OL,3,CWild beavers found following 'illegal
OL,4,Cand unauthorised releases'
OL,6,FMr Varley said: "Cumbria Connect does
OL,7,Fnot support illegal wildlife releases
OL,8,Fand believes species recovery must
OL,9,Ftake place through responsible,
OL,10,Flicensed and transparent processes
OL,11,Finvolving local communities, statutory
OL,12,Fagencies and land managers."
OL,14,FHe warned some groups believe
OL,15,Freleasing beavers through the proper
OL,16,Fprocess is too slow, and carry out
OL,17,Fillegal beaver releases.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,358,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1779185247
OL,3,CWild beavers found following 'illegal
OL,4,Cand unauthorised releases'
OL,6,FMr Varley said: "They might just come
OL,7,Falong and put them into the river and
OL,8,Fthe disappear, and that's really hard
OL,9,Fon the animals because there could be
OL,10,Fa welfare issue for them: if there's
OL,11,Fonly one family how are they going to
OL,12,Freproduce?"
OL,14,FIn Scotland, beavers have been
OL,15,Freleased into the wild since 2009, and
OL,16,Fthe country now has more than 2000
OL,17,Fbeavers.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
