PN,35706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F357A1779185247
OL,3,CWild beavers found following 'illegal
OL,4,Cand unauthorised releases'
OL,6,FIn England, however, the first wild
OL,7,Fbeaver release only took place earlier
OL,8,Fthis year after rules were changed in
OL,9,F2025.
OL,11,FCumbria Connect is now working with
OL,12,Forganisations, including Natural
OL,13,FEngland, to find a long-term approach
OL,14,Fto managing the population.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
